1 othe r election as designated by the Secretary of the State Election
2 Board as provided in subsection D of this section, by electronic
3 mail or by other means of electronic communication in a form and
4 manner prescribed by the Secretary of the State Election Board, if
5 the voter:
6 1. Is a Federal Post Card Application registrant and is
